title: E134 LOGAN PAUL LET EVERYONE DOWN - IMPAULSIVE EP. 134
itunes:title: LOGAN PAUL LET EVERYONE DOWN - IMPAULSIVE EP. 134
description:
Coming off his controversial loss to KSI, Logan Paul attempts to revive his career with yet another episode of IMPAULSIVE... Jake Paul is a crybaby? Logan had wet dreams before the fight? Spencer got a haircut? The new Ranch is haunted? What’s next for Team Maverick? So many questions you’ll never need to know the answer to...
